y operation”</a></li></ul><ul class="list-unstyled" data-level="h2"><li data-target="#ref354587"><a class="w-100" href="/event/2022-Russian-invasion-of-Ukraine#ref354587">The Battle of Kyiv and the initial Russian advance</a></li></ul><ul class="list-unstyled" data-level="h2"><li data-target="#ref354588"><a class="w-100" href="/event/2022-Russian-invasion-of-Ukraine#ref354588">The refugee crisis and evidence of Russian war crimes</a></li></ul></div></li><li data-target="#ref354589"><div class="d-flex align-items-center"><button class="h1-link-drawer-button btn btn-xs btn-circle d-flex rounded" type="button" aria-label="Toggle Heading"><em class="material-icons font-18" data-icon="keyboard_arrow_right"></em></button><a class="w-100" href="/event/2022-Russian-invasion-of-Ukraine#ref354589">International support for Ukraine</a></div><div class="ml-40 toc-drawer sub-toc-drawer"><ul class="list-unstyled" data-level="h2"><li data-target="#ref354590"><a class="w-100" href="/event/2022-Russian-invasion-of-Ukraine#ref354590">Zelensky appeals to the West, the sinking of the <em>Moskva</em>, and the fall of Mariupol</a></li></ul><ul class="list-unstyled" data-level="h2"><li data-target="#ref354591"><a class="w-100" href="/event/2022-Russian-invasion-of-Ukraine#ref354591">The isolation of Russia and the expansion of NATO</a></li></ul><ul class="list-unstyled" data-level="h2"><li data-target="#ref354592"><a class="w-100" href="/event/2022-Russian-invasion-of-Ukraine#ref354592">Russian disinformation and the meme war</a></li></ul></div></li><li data-target="#ref354593"><div class="d-flex align-items-center"><button class="h1-link-drawer-button btn btn-xs btn-circle d-flex rounded" type="button" aria-label="Toggle Heading"><em class="material-icons font-18" data-icon="keyboard_arrow_right"></em></button><a class="w-100" href="/event/2022-Russian-invasion-of-Ukraine/The-Ukrainian-counterattack">The Ukrainian counterattack</a></div><div class="ml-40 toc-drawer sub-toc-drawer"><ul cl